Package hospitalsystem.data

Class Database

java.lang.Object
hospitalsystem.data.Database
public class Database extends Object
Database management class for the hospital system. Handles all data persistence operations including loading from and saving to CSV files, and maintains in-memory data structures for various hospital system entities. This class provides centralized data management for: - Users (Patients, Doctors, Administrators, Pharmacists) - Medical Inventory - Appointments - Replenishment Requests
Since:
2024-11-19
Author:
An Xian, Gracelynn, Leo
